h API: GET /api/v1/foods/search with PostgreSQL full-text search, fuzzy ranking (recent > exact > verified > branded), multi-language via nameTranslations JSONB, pagination\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-010\"\n  description: \"Food detail, recent, favorites API: GET /api/v1/foods/:id, /recent, /favorites, POST/DELETE /favorites/:foodId\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-011\"\n  description: \"Barcode lookup API: GET /api/v1/foods/barcode/:barcode — local DB first, Open Food Facts fallback, error code barcode_not_found\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-051\"\n  description: \"Custom food CRUD API: POST /api/v1/foods (CreateFoodDto, source=user_created), PUT /api/v1/foods/:id (own foods only), DELETE /api/v1/foods/:id (own foods only)\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-012\"\n  description: \"Meal entry CRUD API: POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/logs/:date/meals with computed macro snapshot (calories, protein, carbs, fat, fiber) stored on write\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Meal Logging\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 4\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-013\"\n  description: \"Water entry API: POST/DELETE /api/v1/logs/:date/water\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Meal Logging\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 4\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-014\"\n  description: \"Daily log API: GET /api/v1/logs/:date — returns DailySummary (computed query, not stored): meals by slot, water entries, weight entry, activities, calorie/macro totals vs targets\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Daily Log Response\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 4\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-015\"\n  description: \"Today dashboard UI (S-DASH-1): calorie ring (180px mobile / 220px tablet, amber fill, overflow → rose-500 ring + text, 600ms ease-out fill animation, tap → nutrition breakdown), macro bars (4 bars, spec colors, tap → sources), meal cards per slot, S-DASH-2 slot expansion (all entries, macros per row, swipe edit/delete), hydration tile (+250ml/+500ml quick-add), weight tile, activity tile, day swipe navigation, pull-to-refresh\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-DASH-1\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-016\"\n  description: \"Food search UI (S-LOG-6, S-LOG-7): search bar (autofocus), filter chips (All/My Foods/Branded/Generic), results list with name/brand/kcal, serving picker dropdown, quantity input, live macro preview, meal slot selector, add button\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-6\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-017\"\n  description: \"Log entry point modal (S-LOG-1): bottom sheet on mobile / side panel on tablet+, 4 options (Photo/Barcode/Search/Voice), recent entries (last 5, tap to re-log), favorite foods\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-1\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-018\"\n  description: \"Journal/food log screen (S-JOURNAL-1): calendar strip (weekly view), day totals (kcal/protein/carbs/fat), meals accordion (breakfast/lunch/dinner/snacks), full nutrition line per entry, edit/delete per entry, copy day to today, pull-to-refresh; empty state: 'Start your day — log your first meal' + Log food CTA\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-JOURNAL-1\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-032\"\n  description: \"Barcode scanner UI (S-LOG-4, S-LOG-5): camera viewfinder with ZXing barcode overlay, 'Enter barcode manually' fallback, product detail sheet (name/brand, nutrition per 100g + per serving, serving picker, quantity input, meal slot selector, add button)\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-4\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-052\"\n  description: \"Custom food creation screen (S-LOG-9): form with name, brand (optional), serving size label + weight, nutrition per 100g (calories, protein, carbs, fat, fiber, sugar, sodium optional). Saves to 'My Foods' (source=user_created). Accessible from food search results when food not found.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-9\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M2: Profile & Personalization ──────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-019\"\n  description: \"Onboarding flow UI (S-AUTH-2, S-AUTH-3): 6-step wizard — goal / demographics (age, sex, height, weight) / activity level / dietary restrictions + allergies / target weight + pace / summary. Thin progress bar (not stepper), one question per screen, immediate highlight on selection, final screen animates calorie number counting up to target.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-AUTH-2\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-020\"\n  description: \"TDEE calculation engine: Mifflin-St Jeor BMR (sex-specific), activity multiplier, calorie target per goal (maintain/lose/build), default macro split (protein 20% / fat 30% / carbs 50% per WHO/DRI). Manual macro override with redistribution: editing one macro auto-recalculates remaining calories across the others.\"\n  source: \"spec/02-data-models.md:§Calorie Calculation (TDEE)\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-021\"\n  description: \"Profile API: GET /api/v1/profile, PUT /api/v1/profile, 