setup + initial migration: User, UserProfile, DailyTargets, Food (with nameTranslations JSONB + micronutrients JSONB), ServingSize, MealEntry, WaterEntry, WeightEntry, ActivityEntry, Exercise, FavoriteRecipes tables\"\n  source: \"spec/02-data-models.md:§Core Models\"\n  milestone: \"M0\"\n  lane: 1\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-004\"\n  description: \"Better Auth integration: email/password register, login, logout, refresh, forgot/reset password, JWT session middleware\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Auth\"\n  milestone: \"M0\"\n  lane: 1\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-005\"\n  description: \"Design system: Tailwind theme with spec tokens (Primary #16A34A, Accent #F59E0B, macro colors: Protein #3B82F6 / Carbs #A855F7 / Fat #EF4444 / Fiber #10B981), Inter variable font, 4px spacing grid, border-radii (sm:6px md:12px lg:16px xl:24px full:9999px), shadcn/ui base components (Button, Input, Card, Dialog, Sheet, Toast). NO traffic-light food classification.\"\n  source: \"spec/06-ux-design.md:§Design System\"\n  milestone: \"M0\"\n  lane: 2\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-006\"\n  description: \"App shell: responsive layout — bottom tab bar 5 items (mobile), collapsible left sidebar (tablet/desktop), global FAB '+' button, routing structure, layout breakpoints (mobile <640px / tablet 640-1024px / desktop >1024px)\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§Navigation Structure\"\n  milestone: \"M0\"\n  lane: 2\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-007\"\n  description: \"Auth screens: Landing/Welcome (S-AUTH-1) with 'Get Started', 'Sign In', 'Continue as Guest' options; Login (S-AUTH-4) with email/password + forgot password; account creation form\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§AUTH SCREENS\"\n  milestone: \"M0\"\n  lane: 2\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-050\"\n  description: \"Client library setup: Zustand store scaffold, TanStack Query provider + query client config with optimistic mutation helpers (log entries appear instantly, rollback on error), React Hook Form + Zod validation utilities\"\n  source: \"spec/05-tech-stack.md:§Frontend\"\n  milestone: \"M0\"\n  lane: 2\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-053\"\n  description: \"Guest mode: 'Continue as Guest' flow from S-AUTH-1, IndexedDB-first data path via Dexie.js for all meal/water/weight entries, persistent non-intrusive 'Back up your data →' banner (no forced signup prompts), guest-to-account upgrade with data migration\"\n  source: \"spec/03-user-flows.md:§Flow 1\"\n  milestone: \"M0\"\n  lane: 2\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M1: Core Log Loop ──────────────────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-008\"\n  description: \"Food DB seeding script: import USDA FoodData Central (generic foods, micronutrients) + Open Food Facts top 50k (branded, barcodes) into foods/serving_sizes tables; pnpm db:seed loads ~10k curated foods + demo user\"\n  source: \"spec/05-tech-stack.md:§Food Database Strategy\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-009\"\n  description: \"Food search API: GET /api/v1/foods/search with PostgreSQL full-text search, fuzzy ranking (recent > exact > verified > branded), multi-language via nameTranslations JSONB, pagination\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-010\"\n  description: \"Food detail, recent, favorites API: GET /api/v1/foods/:id, /recent, /favorites, POST/DELETE /favorites/:foodId\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-011\"\n  description: \"Barcode lookup API: GET /api/v1/foods/barcode/:barcode — local DB first, Open Food Facts fallback, error code barcode_not_found\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-051\"\n  description: \"Custom food CRUD API: POST /api/v1/foods (CreateFoodDto, source=user_created), PUT /api/v1/foods/:id (own foods only), DELETE /api/v1/foods/:id (own foods only)\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Food Database\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 3\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-012\"\n  description: \"Meal entry CRUD API: POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/logs/:date/meals with computed macro snapshot (calories, protein, carbs, fat, fiber) stored on write\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Meal Logging\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 4\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-013\"\n  description: \"Water entry API: POST/DELETE /api/v1/logs/:date/water\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Meal Logging\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 4\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-014\"\n  description: \"Daily log API: GET /api/v1/logs/:date — returns DailySummary (computed query, not stored): meals by slot, water entries, weight entry, activities, calorie/macro totals vs targets\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Daily Log Response\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 4\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-015\"\n  description: \"Today dashboard UI (S-DASH-1): calorie ring (180px mobile / 220px tablet, amber fill, overflow → rose-500 ring + text, 600ms ease-out fill animation, tap → nutrition breakdown), macro bars (4 bars, spec colors, tap → sources), meal cards per slot, S-DASH-2 slot expansion (all entries, macros per row, swipe edit/delete), hydration tile (+250ml/+500ml quick-add), weight tile, activity tile, day swipe navigation, pull-to-refresh\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-DASH-1\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-016\"\n  description: \"Food search UI (S-LOG-6, S-LOG-7): search bar (autofocus), filter chips (All/My Foods/Branded/Generic), results list with name/brand/kcal, serving picker dropdown, quantity input, live macro preview, meal slot selector, add button\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-6\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-017\"\n  description: \"Log entry point modal (S-LOG-1): bottom sheet on mobile / side panel on tablet+, 4 options (Photo/Barcode/Search/Voice), recent entries (last 5, tap to re-log), favorite foods\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-1\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-018\"\n  description: \"Journal/food log screen (S-JOURNAL-1): calendar strip (weekly view), day totals (kcal/protein/carbs/fat), meals accordion (breakfast/lunch/dinner/snacks), full nutrition line per entry, edit/delete per entry, copy day to today, pull-to-refresh; empty state: 'Start your day — log your first meal' + Log food CTA\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-JOURNAL-1\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-032\"\n  description: \"Barcode scanner UI (S-LOG-4, S-LOG-5): camera viewfinder with ZXing barcode overlay, 'Enter barcode manually' fallback, product detail sheet (name/brand, nutrition per 100g + per serving, serving picker, quantity input, meal slot selector, add button)\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-4\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-052\"\n  description: \"Custom food creation screen (S-LOG-9): form with name, brand (optional), serving size label + weight, nutrition per 100g (calories, protein, carbs, fat, fiber, sugar, sodium optional). Saves to 'My Foods' (source=user_created). Accessible from food search results when food not found.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-9\"\n  milestone: \"M1\"\n  lane: 5\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M2: Profile & Personalization ──────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-019\"\n  description: \"Onboarding flow UI (S-AUTH-2, S-AUTH-3): 6-step wizard — goal / demographics (age, sex, height, weight) / activity level / dietary restrictions + allergies / target weight + pace / summary. Thin progress bar (not stepper), one question per screen, immediate highlight on selection, final screen animates calorie number counting up to target.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-AUTH-2\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-020\"\n  description: \"TDEE calculation engine: Mifflin-St Jeor BMR (sex-specific), activity multiplier, calorie target per goal (maintain/lose/build), default macro split (protein 20% / fat 30% / carbs 50% per WHO/DRI). Manual macro override with redistribution: editing one macro auto-recalculates remaining calories across the others.\"\n  source: \"spec/02-data-models.md:§Calorie Calculation (TDEE)\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-021\"\n  description: \"Profile API: GET /api/v1/profile, PUT /api/v1/profile, POST /api/v1/profile/recalculate-targets (recomputes DailyTargets from current UserProfile)\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§User Profile\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-022\"\n  description: \"Profile editor UI (S-PROFILE-1, S-PROFILE-2): goals editor, body metrics, dietary preferences + allergies, notification settings (per-slot meal reminder schedule), units/language selector, recalculate targets button with live preview\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-PROFILE-1\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-023\"\n  description: \"Wire dashboard calorie ring and macro bars to user's personal DailyTargets; ring + bars show target-relative progress once onboarding is complete\"\n  source: \"spec/08-milestones.md:§Milestone 2\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-055\"\n  description: \"Account deletion: DELETE /api/v1/users/me (purges all user data + entries), 'Delete all data' and 'Account deletion' actions in S-PROFILE-3 with confirmation dialog; full S-PROFILE-3 screen (export + delete all data + account deletion + privacy policy link)\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-PROFILE-3\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-058\"\n  description: \"Weekly check-in interactive flow (Flow 6): BullMQ weekly-summary job triggers notification → weigh-in prompt screen (current weight input, delta from last week displayed) → optional goal pace adjustment if off-track → lesson recommendation based on progress\"\n  source: \"spec/03-user-flows.md:§Flow 6\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 6\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M2+: Weight & Activity ─────────────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-024\"\n  description: \"Weight logging API + UI: POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/logs/:date/weight, weight tile quick-log modal on dashboard\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Meal Logging\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 7\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-025\"\n  description: \"Activity logging API + UI: POST/PUT/DELETE /api/v1/logs/:date/activities, exercise search GET /api/v1/exercises, activity log modal (search exercises, duration input, intensity selector, MET-based calorie estimate), activity tile on dashboard\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Exercises\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 7\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-026\"\n  description: \"Exercise DB seed: 200+ activities with MET values across cardio, strength, flexibility, sports, daily_activity categories\"\n  source: \"spec/01-features.md:§F7\"\n  milestone: \"M2\"\n  lane: 7\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M3: AI Food Recognition ────────────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-027\"\n  description: \"MinIO service in Docker Compose + file upload API: POST /api/v1/photos/upload (multipart, temp bucket, returns objectKey)\"\n  source: \"spec/05-tech-stack.md:§Photo Recognition Flow\"\n  milestone: \"M3\"\n  lane: 8\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-028\"\n  description: \"BullMQ analyze-photo job: enqueue on upload, status tracking via SSE endpoint GET /api/v1/photos/:jobId/status, returns [{name, weightG, confidence}]\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Photo Recognition\"\n  milestone: \"M3\"\n  lane: 8\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-029\"\n  description: \"Vision provider integrations: Ollama (LLaVA/moondream2, local) as Option A, OpenAI GPT-4o Vision as Option B, Gemini Flash (free tier) as Option C. VISION_PROVIDER=ollama|openai|gemini env switch. Structured output: JSON [{name, weightG, confidence}].\"\n  source: \"spec/05-tech-stack.md:§AI / Food Recognition\"\n  milestone: \"M3\"\n  lane: 8\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-030\"\n  description: \"Photo capture UI (S-LOG-2) + recognition results screen (S-LOG-3): full-screen camera viewfinder, gallery picker, capture → loading state (SSE poll) → results list (editable name, editable weight spinner, live kcal preview, remove button), 'Add item manually' button, meal slot selector, confirm\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-2\"\n  milestone: \"M3\"\n  lane: 8\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-031\"\n  description: \"Voice input UI (S-LOG-8): Web Speech API, animated waveform, live transcription display, recognized item chips (editable), confirm flow → adds to selected meal slot\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-LOG-8\"\n  milestone: \"M3\"\n  lane: 8\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-056\"\n  description: \"Quick-add free-text NLP parsing: text input 'two eggs and oatmeal 80g', LLM/regex parse → bulk-populate food search suggestions with estimated weights, user confirms each item before adding to meal\"\n  source: \"spec/01-features.md:§F2.5\"\n  milestone: \"M3\"\n  lane: 8\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M4: Analytics ──────────────────────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-033\"\n  description: \"Analytics API: GET /api/v1/analytics/summary (calories/macros by date range), /nutrients (micro + macro vs RDA), /weight (daily entries + trend), /foods/top (most logged), /meals/timing (entries bucketed by hour-of-day)\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Analytics\"\n  milestone: \"M4\"\n  lane: 9\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-034\"\n  description: \"Analytics charts UI (S-PROGRESS-1): time range picker (7d/30d/3m/1y), calorie bar chart + target line, macro stacked area, weight scatter + trend line, nutrient coverage horizontal bars (vs RDA), water intake trend, meal timing heatmap (when in day user eats). Empty state when <3 days logged: 'Log for 3+ days to see trends' + Go to journal CTA.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-PROGRESS-1\"\n  milestone: \"M4\"\n  lane: 9\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-035\"\n  description: \"Streak calculation engine: rule = ≥1 food entry logged = streak day (no calorie-target pressure). Badge on dashboard header with bounce + subtle confetti on new streak day.\"\n  source: \"spec/01-features.md:§F3\"\n  milestone: \"M4\"\n  lane: 9\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-036\"\n  description: \"Data export API + UI: GET /api/v1/export/json, /csv — full user data. Export button on S-PROFILE-3.\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Data Export\"\n  milestone: \"M4\"\n  lane: 9\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-054\"\n  description: \"Nutrient deep-dive screen (S-PROGRESS-2): nutrient selector (macro or micro), daily breakdown chart, top food sources for selected nutrient. Linked from nutrient coverage bars in S-PROGRESS-1.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-PROGRESS-2\"\n  milestone: \"M4\"\n  lane: 9\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M5: Coach / Content ────────────────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-037\"\n  description: \"Lesson + LessonProgress Drizzle schema + migrations; lesson API: GET /api/v1/lessons (browse), /:id, /today (queue of 2-3), POST /:id/complete, GET /progress (by category)\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Educational Content\"\n  milestone: \"M5\"\n  lane: 10\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-038\"\n  description: \"Lesson seed data: 20+ open-licensed articles across all 6 categories: nutrition, sleep, stress, habits, fitness, mindfulness\"\n  source: \"spec/01-features.md:§F5\"\n  milestone: \"M5\"\n  lane: 10\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-039\"\n  description: \"Coach home UI (S-COACH-1): today queue (2-3 cards), continue learning section, category browse (6 categories). Lesson detail (S-COACH-2): title, read time, cover illustration, markdown body render, mark complete button, related lessons. Empty state when all done: 'You've completed today's lessons. Come back tomorrow.' + Browse all CTA.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-COACH-1\"\n  milestone: \"M5\"\n  lane: 10\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-040\"\n  description: \"Recipe + RecipeIngredient Drizzle schema + migration; recipe API: GET /api/v1/recipes (browse + filter), /:id, POST (create), PUT /:id, DELETE /:id, POST /:id/favorite, DELETE /:id/favorite, POST /:id/log (creates MealEntries for all ingredients in selected meal slot)\"\n  source: \"spec/07-api.md:§Recipes\"\n  milestone: \"M5\"\n  lane: 11\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-041\"\n  description: \"Recipe seed data: 30+ recipes with ingredients linked to food DB; macros per serving auto-calculated from RecipeIngredient weights\"\n  source: \"spec/01-features.md:§F6\"\n  milestone: \"M5\"\n  lane: 11\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-042\"\n  description: \"Recipe browser UI (S-COACH-3): grid/list toggle, filter bar (diet type, prep time, calorie range), recipe cards. Recipe detail (S-COACH-4): hero image, macros per serving, serving selector (scales ingredients), ingredients list, step-by-step instructions, 'Log this meal' button → meal slot picker, favorite toggle, custom recipe builder (add food DB items as ingredients, auto-calculate macros). Empty state (no favorites): 'Save recipes you love here' + Browse recipes CTA.\"\n  source: \"spec/04-screens.md:§S-COACH-3\"\n  milestone: \"M5\"\n  lane: 11\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n# ── M6: PWA & Polish ──────────────────────────────────────────\n\n- id: \"CHK-043\"\n  description: \"Service worker (Workbox/next-pwa): offline read cache for dashboard + journal + recipes, install prompt (Add to Home Screen)\"\n  source: \"spec/08-milestones.md:§Milestone 6\"\n  milestone: \"M6\"\n  lane: 12\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-044\"\n  description: \"Background sync + Dexie.js offline store: queue log entries while offline, sync to server on reconnect, offline indicator banner when no connection\"\n  source: \"spec/05-tech-stack.md:§Frontend\"\n  milestone: \"M6\"\n  lane: 12\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-045\"\n  description: \"Push notifications: per-slot meal reminders (configurable schedule from CHK-022 settings), weekly check-in prompt\"\n  source: \"spec/08-milestones.md:§Milestone 6\"\n  milestone: \"M6\"\n  lane: 12\n  status: \"pending\"\n  test: null\n  commit: null\n\n- id: \"CHK-057\"\n  descripti